        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 5,
            "text": "Then, no way, they are going to know"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 6,
            "text": "Did We not make the earth a bed (to rest on)"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 7,
            "text": "and the mountains as pins"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 8,
            "text": "And We created you in pairs"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 9,
            "text": "And We made your sleep as a rest"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 10,
            "text": "And We made the night as a cover"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 11,
            "text": "And We made the day as a livelihood (to earn a living)"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 12,
            "text": "And We built seven stable (skies) above you"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 13,
            "text": "And We made (sun) a glowing lamp"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 14,
            "text": "And We sent down plenty of rain from the dense clouds"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 15,
            "text": "that We bring out with it grain and plant"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 16,
            "text": "and dense (and luxurious) gardens"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 17,
            "text": "Indeed the day of separation/decision is an appointed time"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 18,
            "text": "A day when the trumpet is blown and you come in bunches"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 19,
            "text": "And the sky is opened and becomes gates"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 20,
            "text": "and the mountains are moved and become a mirage"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 21,
            "text": "Indeed hell is an ambush"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 22,
            "text": "as a place of return for the rebellious ones"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 23,
            "text": "staying in it for a long time"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 24,
            "text": "They do not taste anything cool or any drink in it"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 25,
            "text": "except boiling water and pus"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 26,
            "text": "An appropriate punishment"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 27,
            "text": "They were not expecting an accounting"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 28,
            "text": "and they strongly denied Our signs"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 29,
            "text": "while We keep track of everything in a book"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 78,
            "verse": 30,
            "text": "So taste (the punishment), for We never add anything to you except punishment"
        }
